close_reason: "Imported pm issue/history files were audited, found free of credential-like private data, and are ready to be committed and pushed."
body: "User asked that the imported .agents/pm/issues and .agents/pm/history files be versioned as well. Audit them for private data first, then commit and push only if clean."
